    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tu ne jafchut ehdis un\npee-ehdis/ un labbus Nammus\nustalsijs un eefsch teem dsihwo-\ndams/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tawi Wehrfchi un fih-\nfi Lohpi buhs wairojfchees / un\ntaws Sudrabs un Selts wairo-\njees/un wiſs/kas tew peederr buhs\nwairojees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawa Sir̈ds pehz leppo-\nfees / un tu aiswirfifi to KUNGU\ntawn Deewu / kas tew no Egip-\ntes - Semnes no ta Wehrgu-\nNamina isweddis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas tew irr waddijs tai-\nleela un breeſmigā Tukfnefi / kur\ndeggofchas Tschuhſchkas un\nSkarpiji un Twihfschana / kur\nUhdens ne bija / kas tew Uhdeni\niswedde no ta zeeta Akmina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas tew Tukfnefi pee-eh-\ndinaja ar Mannu/ ko tawi Tehwi\nne bij pasinnufschi/ ka wiꞥſch tew\nmehrdetu / un ka wiꞥſch tew kahr-\ndinatu / ka wiꞥſch lihds Gallam\ntew labbi darritu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nu ne fakft fawā\nSir̈di: Mans Spehks un man-\nnas Rohkas Stiprums irr man\nfcho Uswarrefchanu dewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet atgahdajees / ka tas\nKUNGS taws Deews tas irr/\nkas tew Spehku dohd tahdu Us-\nwarrefchanu dabbuht / tadeht ka\nwiꞥſch fawu Derrbu apstiprina/\n*o wiꞥſch tarveem Tehweem sweh-\n$/ ittin ka tas schodeen irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja tu to KUNGU ta-\ntas KUNGS tew irr runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "teem kalpoti/ un preeſch winneem\nflannifees / tad apleezinaju es\nschodeen prett jums/ ka juhs nih-\nzin isnihkfeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itt ka tee Pagani / ko ta-\nKUNGS juhsfu Preeſchaā isnth-\nzina / ta patt juhs isnihkfeet / ta-\npehz ka juhs ta KUNGA juhsfu\nDeewa Balkfnei ne effat pa-\nclautigi bijuscht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta IX. Nodalla.\nMohsus mahza / ka laudim ne buhsfawas pa-\nfchas Taiynibas pehz nepateefi leeitees: 1 / 4\nPeeminn teem winnu Pahrgalwibu : 6. Un\ndaschadas Pahrfkahpschanas : 8 / 16 / 20 / 22.\nUn ka wiꞥſch tohs pee Deewa aisluhbſis un\nDeewa Duſmibu nowehrſis : 18 / 25.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lausajs Israēls / tew\nschodeen irr ja-eet pahr to\nJardanu/ ka tu nahz ee-\nmantoht leelas un jo stipras Tan-\ntas / ne ka tu effi / leelus un libd\nDebbehim apstiprinatus Pillsfah-\ntus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Leelus un garrus Laudis /\nEenakima Behrnus/ no ka tu fin-\nnt un dsirdejs effi : Kas warretu\npastahweht Eenaka Behrnu\nPreeſchaā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tew buhs schodeen at-\nsiht / ka tas KUNGS taws\nDeews / tas tahds irr / kas tawa\nPreeſchaā eet / weens aprihjams\nUgguns/tas winnas isdeldehs/un\ntas nomettihs tohs tawa Pree-\nschā / un tu isdshti tohs / un is-\nnihzinafi tohs peepeſchi / ittin ka\n"
    }
  ],
